headline: MTCH Investors Have Opportunity to Join Match Group, Inc. Fraud Investigation with the Schall Law Firm
summary: LOS ANGELES, Nov. 22, 2024 /PRNewswire/ -- The Schall Law Firm, a national shareholder rights litigation firm, announces that it is investigating claims on behalf of investors of Match Group, Inc. ...
